reviews.text:
As an old customer of over 3 years, two professional nail artist Jessie and Na Na has been with me since then.  Their attention to detail, skill, and personalized approach have consistently delivered beautiful, professional results that I've always been extremely satisfied with. Jessie and Na Na are true artists when it comes to manicures - they clearly take pride in their work and go above and beyond to ensure their clients leave feeling confident and happy with their nails. The level of care and artistry they put into each service is truly impressive.

I've always felt welcomed and well cared for during my appointments.  They treated me like a valued, long-term customer, remembering my preferences and making sure I left looking and feeling my best.
Had a lovely mani pedi at Pretticure. The staff are very helpful and professional. A big thank you to Chloe, NaNa, Jess and Jessie! They all made the experience so positive and relaxing.

My mum and I have been coming to Pretticure for many years and have always had the best service and professional pedicure done! Another wonderful session today with Jessie and Nana, aways such an enjoyable time with them!
I've been going to Prettucure for many years now. Both Jessie and Nana are incredibly professional and always offer great advice on colors and designs that suit me. I highly recommend them.
Always delighted to have my mani and pedicure done at Pretticure. The crew are always cheerful and polite. Big shout out to Jessie and Nana who are gentle, patient and skillful. 100% satisfactions.
